{
  "chapter": 41,
  "chapter_summary": "功亏一篑。王怜花先以酒毒杀了圆脸少女等众女子，随后主张众人趁快活王追击沈浪之机逃走。朱七七坚决不肯弃沈浪而去，熊猫儿起初附和王怜花，却在暗中反算王怜花，将其制服。沈浪被快活王追入快活林，纵身跃上旗杆躲避围攻，与快活王隔空对峙。快活王拉断三弓射不上去，一掌震断旗杆，沈浪借杆倾倒之势撞入屋中躲避。王怜花趁机点倒朱七七想挟持她逃跑，却被熊猫儿反制。熊猫儿痛斥王怜花不仁不义，并表明无论沈浪能否生还，他们都会等到底。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就这样我已心满意足了，怎敢再要求别的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胆小鬼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘不答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你知不知道，你方才若是要求别的，我姐妹也会答应的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "我……我……现在……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你这小傻子，现在已来不及了，倒酒吧。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小傻子……胆小鬼……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我原还有机会，只可惜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "只可惜什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "只可惜……只可惜……只可惜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜可惜——一个男人若是不得不将对自己有意的女子杀死，这实在是件令人非常不愉快的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "你们可知道世上还有什么毒药，毒性发作得比这更快么？我让她们死得如此痛快，总算也对得起她们了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪只怕已该来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "但愿他快些来，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "否则怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "否则我们便已不能等他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "放屁！你这没良心的人，若不是他，你能逃到这里来么？而再等片刻，你……你……你竟敢说不等他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "若不是他，我根本不会落在那白飞飞手中，更不会落在快活王手中。我根本不必感激他！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "这话你方才在他面前为何不说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "只因我不敢说。这回答你够满意了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "我只道你已多少有了些人性，哪知你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "猫儿，你仔细想想，我们多留在此地一刻，只有多增加一分危险。与其大家一齐死在这里，倒不如逃出几个算几个。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你……你怎能说得出这样的话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "这话本是沈浪自己说的，我相信沈浪在这种情况之下，也必定会这样做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "猫儿，你……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "我决不能抛下沉浪。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "你们讲理些好么……现在，快活王的注意力必定全集中在沈浪身上，我们乘机逃出去，希望必定很大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "何况，沈浪若没有我们这些累赘，自己必定也可以逃得出去的，你们难道还信不过他有这力量？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "好，你们走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在这里等他。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "他，他若永远不能来了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还是要等他。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "你要等到什么时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等到死为止。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "你呢？人家是同命鸳鸯，你难道也要陪着她死？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "我陪你走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "这才是男子汉大丈夫的行径。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "这才是够义气的朋友，熊猫儿，我总算认得你了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "滚吧，快滚吧！我……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "text": "你也得陪我们一起滚。",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生，无用的畜生！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "沈浪，到了这时，你还想挣扎，你难道还认为可以逃得了么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "不见棺材不流泪，在下生来就是这种脾气。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "沈浪！你怎的也变得如此愚蠢？你在上面又能耽得几时？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "无论我耽得几时，你敢上来么？你看得见我，却无法上来抓我，岂非痛苦之至？我能眼见你在我脚下痛苦，当真是荣幸得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "你欺我上不去么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "好身法！只是你身法虽妙，也是万万上不来的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "着。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "快活王神力果然惊人，只可惜力气大了些。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "好，沈浪，且叫你瞧瞧本王的手段。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "我正要瞧瞧你这手段。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "围住屋子……看住屋顶……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "沈浪，想不到你居然也会自投死路！不过这也难怪你，你本就已无路可走。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_feng_di_yi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "急风第一骑",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "可要以火攻？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "沈浪，你听着，限你半盏茶功夫，本王数到三，你若还不出来，本王就放火将这屋子烧了，让你化骨扬灰葬身火窟。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_feng_di_yi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "急风第一骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呀沈浪，这回你若还能逃得，我就从这里爬到姑苏去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "猫兄，小弟并无伤她之意，只不过是不忍见她在这里等死而已。此时此刻，她惟有和我们一起逃走才是上策。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "既是如此，咱们快走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "我们就这小山旁绕出去，有烦猫兄探路了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "我抱她，你探路。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "小弟探路也好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "猫——猫兄，你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "你……你不是要跟我一起走么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你若将熊猫儿当作和你一样不仁不义，你便疯了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "猫兄，这是你自己愿意的，小弟并未勉强你……你……你为何出尔反尔，反来暗算小弟？",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "这是我跟你学的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "但……但你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你要别人上当，自己也该上次当了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "熊猫儿居然能令王怜花上当，这真是令人想不到。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你若想得到，还会上当么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "好，我认栽了。你要怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "你若是我又当如何？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "我本当立刻杀了你，只是，此时此刻，我若杀了你，未免要被那快活王笑咱们自相残杀。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "现在，我要你知道两件事：第一，有些人不愿骗人，并非他不会，只不过是不愿意而已，他若愿意时，随时都可骗人的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "这件事我现在已知道得很清楚了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "第二，无论沈浪什么时候回来，咱们都是要等的。沈浪只要有一成逃回来的机会，就值得我们等。世上若有人能令熊猫儿心甘情愿地等他，甚至陪着他死，那人就是沈浪，你明白了么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "明白了，只不过……",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "沈浪只怕连半成逃回来的希望也没有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    }
